=== Fundraising:
My work in leadership of caring for others and raising funds was covered by national and local media.
I organized a fundraising event for my middle school math teacher. Four years after our graduation from middle school, our middle school math teacher, Yuexiao He, was diagnosed with leukemia. I organized 40+ classmates to honor and to care for our teacher. We raised money, hosted an honorary luncheon gathering, and conducted a class visit to our alma mater. Our efforts contributed to attracting coverage from national and local media, which led to more donations and honors for our teacher.
coverage by national media and local media
- [https://news.cntv.cn/20120103/108848.shtml  https://news.cntv.cn/20120103/108848.shtml]
- [https://news.sohu.com/20120628/n346704181.shtml  https://news.sohu.com/20120628/n346704181.shtml]

=== Event planning:

I organized a panel talk that attracted 300+ college students in attendance. The panel’s topic is “Graduate school or job market: Wisdom sharing from our successful senior students”. I organized and hosted this big event. I invited the successful senior students who were just admitted into top graduate programs or landed a job, to share their tried and true wisdom with students. I secured sponsorship from 2 local businesses. This event attracted coverage from local media.

